  "title": "Prime Mover Driver",
  "description": "<p>Responsibilities:</p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Handle daily goods delivery and collection in a timely and accurate manner</li>\n  <li>Loading and unloading of goods safely</li>\n  <li>Basic upkeep and housekeeping of vehicle</li>\n  <li>Responsible for complying with the drivers rules and regulations when driving the company vehicle</li>\n  <li>Other ad hoc duties as and when assigned</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Requirements:</p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Must have valid Class 4 driving licence</li>\n  <li>Diligent, positive work attitude and a team player</li>\n  <li>Have good road safety awareness and practice defensive driving</li>\n  <li>Good time management and attendance records</li>\n</ul>",
